location.fullValue: Eden Cay Plan, The Ranches at Heartland Crossing

data.description: Experience modern comfort in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven where luxury meets functionality. The heart of this home is its updated eat-in kitchen, adorned with sleek black stainless steel appliances, gray cabinets, updated brushed nickel door pulls, new faucet, lighting, back splash and a pantry is included. The open-concept floor plan has a huge great/living room with an modern industrial ceiling fan. The home has trendy gray colors throughout new luxury vinyl plank flooring in the entry, kitchen and bathrooms and boast plush carpeting in the great room and primary bedroom creating coziness and warmth throughout. Outside is a fenced backyard which is located on a pond, providing a peaceful backdrop and excellent for entertaining. The large wooden patio structure  provides shade and shelter from the sun and rain.   The 2-car garage is finished and includes an insulated door. ROOF INSTALLED 2021, NEW WATER HEATER 2020, HVAC NEW 2020, GDO installed 2020, CARPET 2020, LPV 2019, APPLIANCES 2019. Conveniently located close to shopping, dining and entertainment.
